ygData.messageBody:
Hello all
Iv been preety quite this week on the mailing list. Iv been extremly busy at
work and have not had a chance to post.

I cant rember when David said he would be back from his vacation, but David
if you are on this weekend Look me up on Bristlbane and lets see about geting
the Guild started here. Also anyone that Would like to join the guild on here
let me know. I have three chars on the server, but will most likely be
playing two of the three.

Wampir Keogh. most likely will not be playing. (takeing a break)
Windom. slight chance of playing
Zute, Lev 10 Ranger will defently be playing some.

So look me up. Zute is curently residing in West Karena, but thinking about
relocating. Maybe to Freeport, East, West Commons.

If I play Windom he is Defently Relocating. Prey is too spread apart in West
Karena for someone that doesnt have Track.

Well Look me up when you have the time
Look forward to Meeting you all

Wampir
